<div class="server-description">
    <p>The <strong>Apex-MC server</strong> is a vibrant Minecraft community dedicated to providing an exceptional multiplayer experience. Whether you're a seasoned builder or a newcomer exploring Minecraft for the first time, Apex-MC offers a wide range of custom game modes, plugins, and unique worlds tailored to enhance creativity and collaboration. From survival adventures to creative building, we aim to foster a fun, supportive environment where players can build, explore, and connect. Join us on Apex-MC and be part of an evolving world shaped by the community.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="server-features">
    <h2>Game Modes and Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Survival Mode:</strong> Gather resources, build shelters, and survive in a challenging environment.</li>
      <li><strong>Creative Mode:</strong> Unleash your creativity with unlimited resources and build anything you imagine.</li>
      <li><strong>Mini-games:</strong> Enjoy exciting mini-games like SkyWars, Spleef, and Parkour challenges.</li>
      <li><strong>Custom Plugins:</strong> Experience enhanced gameplay with unique server-side plugins.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="community-highlights">
    <h2>Community Highlights</h2>
    <p>At Apex-MC, our community is at the heart of everything we do. Join events, collaborate on massive building projects, or compete in tournaments. Whether you’re here to play or make friends, you’ll find a welcoming and active group of players ready to share the adventure with you.</p>
